读MIS和供应链的博士。以后前途应该大大的，比我强多了。</p><p><br></p><p>我这种家里穷国内硕士出来的只能申到个前100的学校勉强读个博。由于出身不好，能力一般目前找工作的结果已经是我能达到的上限了。我们系里最牛的中国人，而且是女生又漂亮也不过找了个和我这个学校排名一模一样的学校，只不过人家在一线大城市钱多个一万多而已。</p><p><br></p><p>所以出身貌似挺重要，有钱的话读个硕。 </p>", "like_count": 2, "author_name": "匿名用户", "author_id": "", "author_is_anonymous": true}, {"url_token": "zhao-fang-fa-63", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "10143895659", "reply_comment_id": "932015179", "reply_root_comment_id": "931988470", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "答主为什么不申MIS供应链的博？是国内硕很难申吗", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "噜啦啦", "author_id": "e1ced01972bbb6f9fff760f946968e86", "author_is_anonymous": false}]}, {"url_token": "shi-tou-59-17-29", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "930980521", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "930980521", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "厉害啊答主，666", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "快乐的小猪", "author_id": "834edfecf0f39807fafadad71a4156a3", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": []}, {"url_token": "diao-ni-xi", "headline": "迪奥丝专业博士", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "930200237", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "930200237", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "<p>威廉斯堡的小学校嘛？</p>", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "梭哈", "author_id": "46492dfcff9ad6fb18900c28827ce6f3", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": []}]